I will review further only after fixing the first review comment.. please

Can u create a python function which can take two, three, four ... threshold values dict and validate..

This is not good idea to have such redundant keywords

Actually these are not an redundant keywords, these will be used for validating sensor threshold values and these keywords will be used based on sensor. An sensor may have either two threshold values, or it can have three threshold values or it may have four or five threshold values like that. it is not like than an sensor should have six threshold values. Hence based on the available threshold values for the particular sensor these keywords were used for validating the sensor threshold.
